title: Bad Actor - As the Curtain Rises!
description:
Floridian Metal fueled by composition, civivs and the complete bastardization of historical truth!

Bad Actor is a brand new metal band self-releasing it's first 8 song EP in 2008. They are from Orlando, Florida and are trying to get some much deserved recognition(if I do say so myself)

2. Sinister Smoke and Smolder
3. Against the Mountain

5. As Meredith Explodes
6. Harem's Hallucination
7. The Kracken of Normandy
8. Ruschak
